quote>有無嘢食推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酸菜大腸米線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今晚就食呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfffc364045c4f10585e7cee8840b129f65af990","tid":15543,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"好正，好鐘意食南記"},{"pid":"f2c48cb158f37256df6d2f57b9bd80f347a7891a","tid":15543,"uid":48261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>春卷點整</blockquote><br />\n上網有講，腐皮包魚肉 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡略講共炸3分半鐘，基本一次炸90條春卷。<br />\n油既處理每間唔太統一，意味千年油。"},{"pid":"fd88293b53e5b17a87f39bd8cf0c0e241ae29239","tid":15543,"uid":48261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好正，好鐘意食南記</blockquote><br />\n食就好食, 但對我黎講做就好悶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bce204b344381a093059ea269f108c60de64c9b","tid":15543,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"做邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解尖沙咀個間次撚次都等半粒鐘都未有野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d126da7f6d844828b4d59657ec9068c369e6fdd4","tid":15543,"uid":126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:35:17.000Z","msg":"點解cut撚左冬菜"},{"pid":"a6f673e55baa2a8b0cec7d7c1d21bdbb1b4548de","tid":15543,"uid":48261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解尖沙咀個間次撚次都等半粒鐘都未有野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔太方便講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀中午一個鐘平均出250碗。 又要品質又要速度應該咁上下。 重點係間舖廚房過半數新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e92f650863a917ed8d6a8496f3028199c56fcef","tid":15543,"uid":48261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解cut撚左冬菜</blockquote><br />\n品質問題喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(好似係)<br />\n唔排除可能你地班撚樣拎太撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申我做果時已經無左了"},{"pid":"ffa3bee0e2baafa9b3f8a1460981399cbf6186b3","tid":15543,"uid":48261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7cbe5eea15774abe7332ae09ac9f9338c7b011","tid":15543,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:00:57.000Z","msg":"上次食到半碗先發現有條頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb581ec551470c0f4c7a6d8b334cb74bf73597ac","tid":15543,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>春卷點整</blockquote><br />\n上網有講，腐皮包魚肉 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡略講共炸3分半鐘，基本一次炸90條春卷。<br />\n油既處理每間唔太統一，意味千年油。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nA瀨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355814a404fc3eeaa075e5b7974cdcf9327caf85","tid":15543,"uid":30512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"點解我幾次夜晚係旺角個間食 成日都有好多毛係入面 眼睫毛頭毛都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但下午茶就冇"},{"pid":"471a4d88614fb491028f1b5304a30357b2c0accf","tid":15543,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:10:41.000Z","msg":"幾時先會開新界區"},{"pid":"fcb18e55eefa569988ee41e07507c84c49038df2","tid":15543,"uid":13809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:13:48.000Z","msg":"南記先係人食，譚仔狗都唔食"},{"pid":"207423930f32f2cee3a9931b23226c46bf444b97","tid":15543,"uid":48655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南記先係人食，譚仔狗都唔食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中環南記兩間都唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}